{"tid":851342,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"【文景之治】[有直播] 港超聯 7/10 14:30 凱景 VS 畜力R&F","createTime":"2018-10-07T05:15:23.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-07T05:47:18.000Z","uid":7439,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"aefad5d930120e9a85e54c45540080224ffe84ab","tid":851342,"uid":7439,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-07T05:15:23.000Z","msg":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\">2018-10-07 14:30<br />\n<strong>中銀人壽香港超級聯賽</strong><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">凱景</span> vs <span style=\"color: navy;\">畜力R&amp;F</span></span> <br />\n深水埗運動場 $80, $30<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://scontent.fhkg4-1.fna.fbcdn.net/v/t1.0-9/43244088_2635534139805689_4010339018725130240_n.jpg?_nc_cat=103&amp;oh=0461f7441dfe37fceb9fb165377f0c71&amp;oe=5C4A3895\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fscontent.fhkg4-1.fna.fbcdn.net%2Fv%2Ft1.0-9%2F43244088_2635534139805689_4010339018725130240_n.jpg%3F_nc_cat%3D103%26oh%3D0461f7441dfe37fceb9fb165377f0c71%26oe%3D5C4A3895&h=345a8af3&s={SIZE}\" /></div>"},{"pid":"4a068b4cd653f01371a849b5092d2d5719a3fe30","tid":851342,"uid":7439,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-07T05:16:31.000Z","msg":"球迷會登記處設於售票處外（停車場入口），而登記處將於上半場開賽後10分鐘關閉，敬請各球迷留意。<br />\n<br />\n2018/2019「凱景球迷會」詳情如下：<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">加入凱景球迷會只需$350，長者、學生、殘疾人士優惠價$200，可享9場聯賽主場賽事門票及打氣tee乙件，希望鼓勵球迷入場與凱景打氣。</span><br />\n<br />\n入會方法：<br />\n凡凱景超聯主場賽事，携同入會費銀行存款紀錄親臨深水埗運動場球迷會攤檔辨理，請預先將會費$350存入凱景體育會的銀行戶口，可獲得主場套票及打氣tee*。<br />\n<br />\n銀行資料：<br />\n中國銀行<br />\nHoi King Sports Association Limited <br />\n01288410437565<br />\n<br />\n註：打氣tee製作需時，約十月頭才有貨。<br />\n<img src=\"https://scontent.fhkg4-1.fna.fbcdn.net/v/t1.0-9/42611805_2618488228176947_4114170780818866176_n.jpg?_nc_cat=111&amp;oh=5508704a504e6f920fdfa9db99866485&amp;oe=5C4A92E7\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fscontent.fhkg4-1.fna.fbcdn.net%2Fv%2Ft1.0-9%2F